TIME_COMPLEXITY = O(n^2)
SPACE_COMPLEXITY = O(k)
Approach : Array sort karo
Taaki two-pointer use kar sake
Example: [-4, -1, -1, 0, 1, 2]
Ek element fix karo (i loop)
Har element ko first number maan lo
Two Pointer lagao
left = i + 1
right = n - 1
Sum check karo
sum = nums[i] + nums[left] + nums[right]
If sum == 0 → answer mil gaya 
If sum < 0 → left++ (sum badhao)
If sum > 0 → right-- (sum kam karo)
Duplicates skip karo
Same triplet repeat na ho